      <title>CIBC将Harry Culham称为下一位首席执行官。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/cibc-names-harry-culham-as-next-ceo-after-long-rise-from-intern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大帝国商业银行任命哈里·库勒姆（Harry Culham）接替首席执行官维克多·多迪格（Victor Dodig），后者将在11月领先美国第五大贷方超过十年后退休。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/cibc-names-harry-culham-as-next-ceo-after-long-rise-from-intern</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着政治风险持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/romanian-inflation-unexpectedly-soars-as-political-risks-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚通货膨胀上个月出乎意料地越来越高，可能会加强中央银行在五月份总统选举之前的价格压力和政治风险而导致的货币宽松措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/romanian-inflation-unexpectedly-soars-as-political-risks-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 07:26:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通策略师说，美国股票夸大衰退风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/us-stocks-bottom-is-probably-here-jpmorgan-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据摩根大通（JPMorgan Chase＆amp;）的说法，美国股票的价格比信贷市场大得多，这给积极的余地留下了惊喜。公司战略家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/us-stocks-bottom-is-probably-here-jpmorgan-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 03:24:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当IEA旗帜贸易战风险面向全球需求时，石油撤退会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源局警告说，消费在贸易战不断升级的压力下，石油倒下了，美国通货膨胀数据刺激了削减收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 23:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票期货在美国生产商价格数据稳定：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者等待查看批发通货膨胀数据是否会证实价格增长放缓的迹象，美国股票期货逐渐消除了较早的巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 22:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
